The post that dismisses the importance of the topic is:

@netflix The year is 2099 and Netflix is gone. Too many people decided to #cancelNetflix due to the serial killing of prestige shows. The return of 1899 was their last hope, so good luck with time travel guys! Now is the right time to #Save1899 Just saying #1899Netflix https://t.co/Ab8zLktgZQ

This post implies that the return of the show "1899" is not important in the grand scheme of things, and dismisses the significance of the campaign to save the show.
